	<h1 class="maintit-e4jadmin">Getting Started</h1>
	<h2 class="sectit-e4jadmin">From the <em>Template Configuration</em> panel:</h2>
	<p class="desc-featured">
		
		1. Choose your color layout<br />
		2. Set your logo <br />
		3. Set the template as Default <br/>
		4. Start to set up your Modules just following the Template documentation, in this way you'll have your website as our demo website.
	</p>
	<div class="warning-msg">If once you've setup the template as Default you'll get a <strong>blank page</strong> in your website, don't worry, everything is working correctly,  you have to start to setup all the modules to let the template works properly. <br /> 
